===Etymology===
From {{etyl|xno|en}} {{term|juel|lang=xno}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|jouel|lang=fro}} (modern [[joyau]]), based ultimately on {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|iocus||joke, jest|lang=la}}.

